@startuml
actor "Project Manager" as PM
participant "Lifecycle & Governance (Agent 09)" as A09
participant "Approval Workflow (Agent 03)" as A03
participant "Workflow Engine (Agent 24)" as A24
participant "Compliance Agent (Agent 16)" as A16
participant "Audit Log" as Audit

PM -> A09: request stage advance
A09 -> A24: evaluate gate criteria
A24 -> A16: run compliance checks
A16 --> A24: compliance result
A24 -> A03: route approvals
A03 -> Audit: log decision
A03 --> A09: approved / rejected
A09 --> PM: stage update
@enduml
